title: DJ Lange Intercity
description:
DJ Lange's Intercity podcasts, starting at 84 and ending at the latest of episode 165 (unfortunately missing 86, 88, and 89).

All episodes are 160kbps quality and were downloaded, for free, directly from www.intercityradio.com.		

There was an issue with the original hash not correctly reporting completed files (even after I forced a recheck, 'my' files were showing as incomplete). (http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9774319/DJ_Lange_Intercity)

Updated to a new hash and also added the 3 hour Mix AHFM 7 Year Anniversary Celebration.

Have this point to the same files and check them so you don't lose your data!
